# ===================== EXECUTIVE SUMMARY =====================
story.append(Paragraph("Executive Summary", styles["H1"]))
story.append(Paragraph(
    "Manual Accounts Payable processing is widely documented as slow and expensive, with industry "
    "benchmarks citing $10\u201315+ per invoice and multi-day cycle times for organizations relying on manual "
    "data entry and 3-way matching. This project designed and built a working prototype of an AI-powered "
    "AP pipeline: invoices are rendered as images, read directly by Claude's vision model (no per-vendor "
    "OCR templates), then validated, matched against purchase orders, and routed to auto-approval or human "
    "review based on configurable business rules.", styles["Body"]))
story.append(Paragraph(
    "The prototype was tested against a deliberately adversarial 13-invoice synthetic batch containing "
    "planted duplicate invoices, PO amount mismatches, an unapproved vendor, and non-PO invoices — to "
    "verify the exception logic, not just the happy path.", styles["Body"]))
