    "correctly routed — 4 to exceptions (the planted error scenarios) and 1 to manual approval (a non-PO "
    "invoice, per policy). Modeled against published industry cost benchmarks, this run's outcome profile "
    "projects to a <b>~72% reduction in processing cost</b> and <b>~82% reduction in processing time</b> "
    "versus a fully manual baseline at equivalent scale. Full methodology and caveats are in Sections 6\u20137.",
    styles["Body"]))
story.append(PageBreak())

